/**
   * Rollback the current IndexWriter. When creating the new IndexWriter use the
   * settings from the given {@link SolrCore}.
   * 
   * @param core
   * @throws IOException
   */
  public abstract void rollbackIndexWriter(SolrCore core) throws IOException;
